<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="perform-v">perform <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /pə'fɔːm/    美 /pər'fɔːrm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-carry-out">1.★ <strong>vt 做；履行；执行 (carry out)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>perform an experiment / an operation / a miracle</strong>
做实验/做手术/创造奇迹</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should <strong>perform</strong> your <strong>duties / promise</strong>. 
你应当履行职责/诺言。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-vt-vi">2.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi表演；演出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The band was going to perform at our local theatre.
乐队将在我们当地剧院演出。</p><footer>2011 山东改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve never seen a Shakespeare’s play performed so wonderfully.
我从没看过表演得如此好的莎士比亚戏剧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>perform perfectly on the piano 
熟练地演奏钢琴</p></div>

<h4 id="3-vi">3.★ <strong>vi 表现；运转：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was disappointed because he had not <strong>performed well</strong> in the sports meeting.
他很失望，因为他在运动会上表现不佳。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The machine is <strong>performing</strong> very <strong>poorly</strong>. 
机器运转非常不正常。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Listening to music at home is one thing, going to hear it <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (perform) live is quite another.  （2015 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. (being) performed  </p></div>